5 SECTION 1. AMENDMENT. Subdivision m of subsection 2 of section 6-09-49 of the North
6 Dakota Century Code is amended and reenacted as follows:
7 m. Critical political subdivision buildings and infrastructure, including correctional
8 facilities; and
9 SECTION 2. TRANSFER - STRATEGIC INVESTMENT AND IMPROVEMENTS FUND -
10 INFRASTRUCTURE REVOLVING LOAN FUND. The office of management and budget shall
11 transfer $50,000,000 from the strategic investment and improvements fund to the infrastructure
12 revolving loan fund during the biennium beginning July 1, 2025, and ending June 30, 2027. The
13 funding transferred pursuant to this section may be used only for loans to political subdivisions
14 for correctional facilities.
